    innerHTML:
      ' <p align="justify"><span><b>(1) </b>Where a person has occupied or permitted the occupancy of a <i>building</i> under Article 1.3.3.1. or 1.3.3.2., such person shall notify the <i>chief building official</i> forthwith upon completion of the <i>building</i>.</span></p> <p align="justify"><span ',
